# Express + No Auth Template

Simple MCP server without authentication - perfect for public APIs and development.

## Quick Start

```bash
git clone <template-repo>
cd <template-repo>
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Environment
```bash
SERVER_URL=http://localhost:3000
PORT=3000
```

## Resource Example
```typescript
const productResource = createResource({
  name: "product",
  schema: ProductSchema,
  uri_template: "products/{id}",
  methods: {
    create: { handler: async (data) => createProduct(data) },
    list: { handler: async () => listProducts() },
    get: { handler: async ({ id }) => getProduct(id) },
    update: { handler: async ({ id, ...data }) => updateProduct(id, data) },
    delete: { handler: async ({ id }) => deleteProduct(id) },
  },
});
```

## Handler Pattern
```typescript
// No authentication - handlers only receive data
handler: async (data) => {
  return await processData(data);
}
```

## Usage
```bash
# No authentication required
curl http://localhost:3000/api/products
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/products -d '{"name":"Product"}'
```
